PreBase is an AI-assisted desktop IDE and code visualization platform.

Long-term vision:
- Combine development, visualization, AI assistance, and deployment.
- Allow developers to understand codebases visually.
- Represent projects as interactive node graphs.
- Eventually evolve into a complete development environment.

Current architecture:
- Electron
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Interactive graph visualization